node.text:
Giving back is something that ROKiT takes great pride in. ROKiT Cities is delivering WiFi connectivity for the residents of Community First! Village, providing affordable, permanent housing, and a supportive community for 200 men and women coming out of chronic homelessness. The connectivity is enabled over installed carrier-grade ROKiT hardware – providing residents with internet access and WiFi calling, ROKiT’s vast 3D movies library, music streaming and more, wherever they are in the 51-acre community. To find out more, check out this short video:
@mobileloaves #keeptalking #ROKiTPhonesUK #3Dsmartphones #wificities #ServingGoodness

node.title: ROKiT Cities installs Free WiFi to Community First! Village in Austin
